{"id": 2661, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些时刻你发现自己的注意力被垄断了？", "description": "注意力即商机，一不小心就掉进“想不关注都难”的圈套。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 14602, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181209195426u2AZJnEIBiUYhm34.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-09T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5035, "title": "哪些时刻你发现自己的注意力被垄断了？", "content": "上网时，你都是怎么发现“自己的注意力被垄断了”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 315165, "content": "即使不关心热点，首页和检索还是会联想显示热搜结果", "image": "img/option/option/201812071326214Doc5EzKBkhG0gAV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315166, "content": "点了“不感兴趣”，信息流广告还是会反复跳出来", "image": "img/option/option/20181207140259UYVGuqFJLPoi8w5K.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315167, "content": "爆款文章被两三个人转了，接下来一天它会密集地出现", "image": "img/option/option/20181207140515Kye6RjkGn0gPU95i.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315169, "content": "本来也没想买啥东西，双11前后还是收到一堆短信推送", "image": "img/option/option/20181207140717Yq4pls28NOSfwKBy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315170, "content": "有热点事件发生，各种公众号都会扎堆围绕它做文章", "image": "img/option/option/20181207141212azMmOkgCi3dWZvIF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315171, "content": "播放一个搞笑视频，看完自动播放无数条相似视频", "image": "img/option/option/20181207141119gLqp6xkZAzfXhJsF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315172, "content": "搜索了一款产品，再打开软件出现无数同款", "image": "img/option/option/20181207142001Hefv1XbwS29Lyzpn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315344, "content": "在线看视频中途弹出的花边广告，还能跟剧情同步互动", "image": "img/option/option/20181207142659bVhMHOnWYS2NEcxl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}